text: Facelina carmelae is a species of sea slug, an aeolid nudibranch, a marine gastropod mollusc in the family Facelinidae.MolluscaBase (2018). Facelina carmelae Moro & Ortea, 2015. Accessed on 2018-02-17. ==Distribution== This species has been reported from Cape Verde. ==References== Category:Facelinidae Category:Gastropods described in 2015 Category:Gastropods of Cape Verde
title: Facelina carmelae
